<scriptment id="42000" point="pazhitnov" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-08-03" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration><comment>Ten seconds.</comment>Yuki watches a television. A Russian man busts into a room in hazard suit, goggles and specialist-gun. He is in a panic.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="pazhitnov" voicelang="ru">There's been a meltdown at the Tetromino Mine!</line>
		<line id="2000" speaker="pazhitnov" voicelang="ru">There will never be another Tetris!</line>
		<line id="3000" speaker="pazhitnov" voicelang="ru">Ever!</line>
		<narration>The Russian's secretary frowns.</narration>
		<line id="4000" speaker="secretary" voicelang="ru">So that's your excuse?</line>
		<narration>Pazhitnov sighs.</narration>
		<line id="5000" speaker="pazhitnov" voicelang="ru">There is no excuse for quitting.</line>
	</part>
</scriptment>